# No Diffs

```terraform
resource "aws_s3_bucket" "one" {
  bucket = "tf-test-bucket-one"
}
```

```hcl

  bucket = "tf-test-bucket-two"
}
```

```tf

  bucket = "tf-test-bucket-three"
}
```

